textAnnotations.description:
Cliprei Prauer Rog
Look into Jese Eyes you will see they are cloed, But as you contimr o look yo will see lis eyes opening
and lookng hack ito your eyes Then go and be ale and kneel on this g of Fah or tooch it to both knres.
Then please check your ceds on tur lener to you. Please return this Prayer Rug Do pot kre t.
